  <div id="main-container" class="main-container container-fluid article-page"><article class="clearfix">
  <header class="article-header">
    <h1>A Movie About Gamergate Is Coming, and Scarlett Johansson Could Be the Lead</h1>
    <div class="by-line">
      <a title="Jack Smith IV's Profile" class="link-author avatar avatar-small" href="../../profiles/188814/jack-smith-iv">
        <img alt="Jack Smith IV's avatar image" class="no-share-btns" src="http://media3.mic.com/ZjNkZjZlNjBhOSMvWkl1N1NvM3VMUVNDYkN0bUE2dV9wVmp0Njl3PS81Mng4ODo4NTF4ODg3LzI1eDI1L2ZpbHRlcnM6cXVhbGl0eSg4NSkvaHR0cHM6Ly9zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tL3BvbGljeW1pYy1pbWFnZXMvZDg2MDZlYTc2MjJmNjk5ZjIyMGEwYzA5MDk3NDBkZDNlMjc1ZmFhZDljZDRjNmMzZjhmNjYwMzFkOTQ5ZmMzYS5qcGc=.jpg">
      </a>
      By
      <a title="Jack Smith IV's Profile" class="link-author name" href="../../profiles/188814/jack-smith-iv">Jack Smith IV</a>
      <time datetime="2015-11-07T00:14:26.000Z" pubdate="">November 07, 2015</time>
    </div>
    <div class="share-facebook-twitter subhead">
      <span class="fb-like-container-text">Like Mic on Facebook:</span>
      <span class="fb-button">
        <div class="fb-like-top fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/thefutureisnowbymic" data-width="300" data-keen-tracking-name="subhed" data-keen-social-channel="facebook_future" data-show-faces="false" data-send="false" data-layout="button"></div>
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div id="article-body" class="article-body share-media-toolbar-block"><div class="share-media share-media-side-fold">
  <ul><li class="share-media-facebook"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128101%2Fa-movie-about-gamergate-is-coming-and-scarlett-johansson-could-be-the-lead" title="Share on Facebook" rel:gt_act="share/facebook/share" rel:gt_label="true" name="fb_share" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-facebook modal-trigger-facebook k-trackable-share" data-fb-link="http://mic.com/articles/128101/a-movie-about-gamergate-is-coming-and-scarlett-johansson-could-be-the-lead" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307534536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-facebook"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>SHARE</a></div></li>
<li class="share-media-twitter"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128101%2Fa-movie-about-gamergate-is-coming-and-scarlett-johansson-could-be-the-lead&amp;original_referer=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128101%2Fa-movie-about-gamergate-is-coming-and-scarlett-johansson-could-be-the-lead&amp;related=MicNews&amp;source=tweetbutton&amp;text=A%20Movie%20About%20Gamergate%20Is%20Coming%2C%20and%20Scarlett%20Johansson%20Could%20Be%20the%20Lead%20by%20%40jacksmithiv&amp;via=MicNews" title="Share on Twitter" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-twitter k-trackable-share" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="twitter" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307534536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-twitter"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>TWEET</a></div></li>
<li class="share-media-tumblr"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://tumblr.com/share/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128101%2Fa-movie-about-gamergate-is-coming-and-scarlett-johansson-could-be-the-lead&amp;description=Awesome.%C2%A0&amp;name=A%20Movie%20About%20Gamergate%20Is%20Coming%2C%20Possibly%20Starring%20Scarlett%20Johansson" title="Share on Tumblr" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-tumblr k-trackable-share" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="tumblr" data-popup-width="450" data-popup-height="483" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307534536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-tumblr"></i><i-social-icon-divider></i-social-icon-divider>POST</a></div></li></ul>
  <div class="corner"></div>
</div>
<div class="article-body-content"><p class="">Few people understand online harassment like Zoë&nbsp;Quinn. As one of the primary targets of Gamergate, she had her personal life and relationships dragged into the spotlight. Soon, she'll be the one broadcasting her story on silver screens across the country.</p>
<p class="">Amy Pascal, former co-chair of Sony Pictures and head of Pascal Pictures, has acquired the rights to Quinn's upcoming memoir,&nbsp;<i>Crash Override: How to Save the Internet From Itself</i>,&nbsp;about nerd culture and the harassment she faced as one of Gamergate's targets. Originally&nbsp;<a href="http://deadline.com/2015/11/zoe-quinn-crash-override-gamergate-memoir-amy-pascal-1201611420/">reported by <i>Deadline</i></a>, Quinn has verified the details to <i>Mic</i>.</p>
<figure contenteditable="false" data-url="https://twitter.com/TheQuinnspiracy/status/662763634766929920" class="embeddable clearfix embeddable-twitter" data-twitterhtml="<blockquote lang=&quot;en&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;><p>Two announcements in one: 1 - I'm publishing a book with Touchstone, a Simon and Schuster imprint 2 - That book is being made into a movie</p><a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/thequinnspiracy/status/662763634766929920&quot;></a><script async=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;></script></blockquote>" id="embeddable-5n7sahg" data-type="twitter"><div class="embeddable-container"><blockquote lang="en" class="twitter-tweet"><p>Two announcements in one: 1 - I'm publishing a book with Touchstone, a Simon and Schuster imprint 2 - That book is being made into a movie</p><a href="https://twitter.com/thequinnspiracy/status/662763634766929920"></a><script async="async" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></blockquote></div></figure>
<p class="">Quinn told&nbsp;<i>Mic </i>the movie isn't about Gamergate exactly but "it's about online harassment and abuse in general." The <a href="http://deadline.com/2015/11/zoe-quinn-crash-override-gamergate-memoir-amy-pascal-1201611420/">original proposal</a> for the movie says:</p>
<blockquote>Gaming and Internet message boards used to be niche interests, mostly for young men. In the past few years, however, they've gone mainstream. Millions of people &mdash; including women and other marginalized people &mdash; have taken an interest in the platforms, image boards, and discussion forums that once belonged by default to a much smaller population. Most gamers give zero fu*ks about this. Like the rest of us, they're just here to play games. But a vocal minority are clinging onto the brand of Cheetos-and-Mountain-Dew exclusionary identity 'hardcore gamer,' muttering 'fu*kin casuals' under their breath.</blockquote>
<p class="">There are few additional details about the film, except that Scarlett Johansson has expressed interest in playing Quinn. The movie will be one of the first films from Pascal Pictures, along with the new <i>Ghostbusters</i>&nbsp;movie starring Kristen Wiig, Melissa McCarthy and&nbsp;Kate McKinnon.</p></div>
<div class="article-items"></div>
